        "id": 1153474
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-04-06T18:59:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t think error checking gets us anything other than complicatiing the code: It\u0027s an easy check, but \u0026act is not user-controlled, and we basically want to ignore EINVAL. I\u0027ll add a comment explaining this.",
      "parentUuid": "d18b84bc_fdcbe65e",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 41,
        "startChar": 2,
        "endLine": 41,
        "endChar": 11
      },
